{"title":"小红帽脱险记  ６","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"６"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他已经到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那黑色的魔手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在推开柴门了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"………！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大白马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从茅屋后面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳了出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准老山妖的背脊骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠命的踢了好几脚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还来不及看清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就被踢倒在地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只哎哟哎哟的叫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不好了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我中了炮弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我痛得不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的肚子炸穿了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬嗬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再也不能吃牛奶鸡蛋了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬嗬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再也装不下又香又甜的白米饭了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大声的哭了起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大白马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高兴着他的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它想唱一个歌儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表示表示它的欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就张开口竖起了尾巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吗哈哈的大叫了一声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活见鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是你这个死老马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那真太不该！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想想看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对你多么好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象客人似的看待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用你驾车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道来往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用你打仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道冲锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是不是把你看得比人还高还重？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你是把我看得高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为你尽的力也不小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为你赚的钱也不少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还贪心不足的鞭打我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几乎要我顶好把性命也送掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄得没有一个人不恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一个人不怨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上就要完蛋了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真该早觉悟，早跑掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这作恶的坏主人谁稀罕！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“笑话，笑话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这真是笑话！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠实的奴才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要反叛了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下真是大变了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我不怕你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我懂得你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天我再来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来一根鞭子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还带来一把青草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你选择那一样好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老子今晚肚子痛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃不成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚一定来把你好好吃一顿。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歪着头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱着眉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手按着肚子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一弯腰的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下山去了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（第三节完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}